@startuml cicd-workflow-logic
!theme plain
title GitHub Actions Workflow 执行逻辑

|触发|
start
:push 到 main/master 分支;

|Build 作业|
:检出代码;
note right: actions/checkout@v4

:设置 Node.js 环境;
note right: actions/setup-node@v4

:安装依赖;
note right: npm ci

:配置 Pages;
note right: actions/configure-pages@v4

:构建项目;
note right: npm run build

:上传构建产物;
note right
  actions/upload-pages-artifact@v3
  path: ./dist
end note

|Deploy 作业|
:等待 Build 完成;
note right: needs: build

:部署到 GitHub Pages;
note right: actions/deploy-pages@v4

:部署完成;
note right
  访问地址:
  https://<user>.github.io/<repo>/
end note

stop
@enduml
